query_id.description: The unique identifier of the query in Looker.

history_created_date.description: The date when the query history entry was created.

history_created_time.description: The date and time when the query history entry was created.

query_model.description: The model name that the query belongs to.

query_view.description: The view name that the query is based on.

space_id.description: The unique identifier of the space where the query was executed.

look_id.description: The unique identifier of the look associated with the query history.

dashboard_id.description: The unique identifier of the dashboard associated with the query history.

user_id.description: The unique identifier of the user who ran the query.

history_query_run_count.description: The number of times the query has been run in the history.

history_total_runtime.description: The total runtime of the query execution in milliseconds.
